Date:   Wed Mar 18 15:58:00 2026 +0100

    Migrate CLI commands from Run to RunE pattern with centralized error handling
    
    - Rename ExitCodeParse to ExitCodeConfig, add new exit codes (Git, NotFound, Validation)
    - Update error categorization to map ParseError to Config, detect FileError.NotFound
    - Rename HandleError to HandleCLIError with cobra.Command parameter
    - Remove HandleValidationErrors, route all errors through HandleCLIError
    - Add IsCobraArgumentError helper for Cobra argument error detection
    - Add ValidationResultError type for wrapping multiple validation errors
    - Convert all commands to RunE pattern (validate, adapt, canonicalize, init, library)
    - Update main.go to use centralized error handling with SetGlobalCommandConfig
    - Update tests to match new exit code mappings (Config=3, Validation=5, NotFound=6)
    - Mark tasks 1.1-2.7 complete in cli-rune-migration change

